ll,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Wxiaoying","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-22","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkErkTa4TORnib3HuKcUyWIwlmcDoT4WTFou6iaTNBOEDZrROibOK2q8yxtTyEPKG63ToL3z7Ho85t5tC/0","content":"不算滑坡谬误，这种效应体现的是世界的关联性。滑坡谬误是强调一连串的必然因果。\n比如大公司出现财务报告造假可能会引起股巿波动或者影响行业行情变动。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1513,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487755026000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"程然","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibeXpgwkiaTloWbvWZibHU3ulLlIhhE6iaIiazJaXkXaYkTTbdwvhdOM7cvxOoQpCxud7DYns8icjZDZ7w/0","content":"不算 因为原句用的是可能 而滑坡谬误是把可能当做必然表述出来","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":714,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487055529000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"貓宁姜","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6agqPwVy4opWYcSWZaVneib0f1rTHkIZ5qhFcGKRAEsbjrQibqJfRIenSXe22uFMgHC2O99xEGECEh6e11rMFfjO9/0","content":"蝴蝶效应是滑坡谬误。\n\n\n蝴蝶偶尔扇动翅膀，只是可能引起龙卷风，但是不存在必然性。那如果蝴蝶效应不是滑坡谬误，那蝴蝶扇动几下翅膀，每时每刻都会引起龙卷风了。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":607,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486703359000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浥尘","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoNL7EDTAve1O74gANzM4RwsvL08Gm6ViarRN6kNic8JzthiapekyDe9cgpm8wiat4QEF78Kvmj4YZ27Y/0","content":"“一只南美洲亚马逊河流域热带雨林中的蝴蝶，偶尔扇动几下翅膀，可能在两周后引起美国德克萨斯引起一场龙卷风。”\n\n这个说法更多的是一种文学的表达，夸张而有戏剧性，常被用作隐喻一个不起眼的细节可能带来结果的巨大改变。个人感觉在文学语境中使用没有问题，但从逻辑的角度严格来说算滑坡谬误，因为没有提到其他必要的因素，并不是每次蝴蝶煽动翅膀都有可能引起龙卷风。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":130,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":148457482200